{"tid":817497,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"綠色和平齊來守護郊野公園！","createTime":"2018-09-13T11:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T12:49:32.000Z","uid":38631,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"86f8ea20025610cf9170d3eb7fef75c0639457a6","tid":817497,"uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4t17Z7WlU7c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4t17Z7WlU7c&d=210pqEY%2F0cwKSZtoy527xQKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=a2d0db99\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4t17Z7WlU7c</a><br />\n<br />\n「這地球，若果有樂園，會像這般嗎？」香港唞氣喘息的淨土，是前人努力耕耘，傳承後代的禮物。為了繁華，我們「摘去鮮花」，為了文明，我們「情願被同化」，難道就是下一代的命運？郊野公園如今危在旦夕，立即聯署，守護屬於未來的樂園：<a href=\"https://act.gp/2Qi8yl9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact.gp%2F2Qi8yl9&d=210pqEY%2F0cwKSZtoy527xQKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=1335c3e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://act.gp/2Qi8yl9</a><br />\n<br />\n土地供應公眾諮詢自4月26日開始，郊野邊陲地帶成為土地供應選項之一。綠色和平不甘下一代的樂園「被同化」，邀請年青指揮家劉卓熙擔任音樂總監，由音樂人伍卓賢改編本地樂隊Shine在2002年發佈的流行曲《燕尾蝶》，與逾20位中小學生新生代組成合唱團，在獅子山、大帽山等郊野公園演唱《燕尾蝶》新章，訴說他們暢遊樂園的願望。<br />\n<br />\n燕尾蝶<br />\n作曲：Barry Chung<br />\n填詞：黃偉文<br />\n改編：伍卓賢 Yin Ng<br />\n監製：劉卓熙 Sanders Lau、伍卓賢 Yin Ng<br />\n<br />\n摘去鮮花　然後種出大廈<br />\n<br />\n那些　胭脂色的　香檳色的　伸手可折的<br />\n段段艷遇　處處有染　都放在眼前<br />\n害怕採花　天黑路遠<br />\n情願對路邊燈飾眷戀<br />\n<br />\n那些　山中開的　天邊飛的　不知所措的<br />\n漸漸熟習　世界會變　不再受驚怕<br />\n為免犧牲　情願被同化<br />\n移徙到鬧市找一個家<br />\n<br />\n燕尾蝶　疲倦了　在偉大佈景下<br />\n這地球　若果有樂園　會像這般嗎<br />\n<br />\n摘去鮮花　然後種出大廈<br />\n文明是種進化　儘管適應　別制止它<br />\n力竭聲沙　情懷承受不起風化<br />\n叢林不割下　如何建造繁華<br />\n別問怎麼不愛它<br />\n蝴蝶夢裡醒來　記不起　對花蕊　有過牽掛<br />\n<br />\n燕尾蝶　存活了　在發射塔之下<br />\n這地球　若果有樂園　會像這般嗎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8516c88cd26da5f02e738bc72885fea29a99f6c","tid":817497,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"一陣又俾班傻閪child登仔盲反"},{"pid":"8262523e140ee4a9e9c925bfb2d01c1a0257fa48","tid":817497,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:00:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edd8aac12b575a66f30101bf0481e44760d41715","tid":817497,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:00:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6033ba5ab59ad415b2a7fd998a7d7bd119853052","tid":817497,"uid":38631,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e8516c88cd26da5f02e738bc72885fea29a99f6c","tid":817497,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"一陣又俾班傻閪child登仔盲反"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:00:57.000Z","msg":"唔係呀嘛<br />\n<br />\n我預自己冇下一代<br />\n都唔想比依一代破壞個剩餘既郊野公園"},{"pid":"7f82f7dcc1cbf81761c74f29473135c1827f7388","tid":817497,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:01:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b69fc79e4aee6f2d313e6dccbb5fbb5fbca6eb14","tid":817497,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:01:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b87236a282cd4cc5cd91a3ed999b02f1037803f","tid":817497,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:01:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d05b97fdad46090af0aefe7cb4b01f49ecb82d2","tid":817497,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:01:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da2ef8882cfde7192e05ec0278d0eeaf04d9e021","tid":817497,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:02:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"556b6de0234ddb6c5f8984c6ba99601c8a5e4c1b","tid":817497,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"